:INFO
Thirty Days Following the Book Exactly
Cal Newport is precise about what deep work requires. I decided to find out if \
following his actual recommendations changed anything real. I blocked my mornings \
for focused work only. I stopped checking email before noon. I scheduled specific \
distraction windows in the afternoon. I kept a shutdown ritual every workday. \
After 30 days I measured what had actually shifted in my output and my stress.

