:JOURNEY
Doing Every Deep Work Exercise
Exercise
Usefulness
- Morning block | 4 | Transformative | Blocking mornings changed my output immediately
- Email boundary | 5 | Highest impact | No email before noon: hardest and best shift
- Shutdown ritual | 4 | Underrated | Verbal close to the day reduced carryover stress
- Digital sabbath | 3 | Still trying | Could not sustain it yet but the goal remains

:CHECKLIST
The Deep Work Protocol I Followed
[x] Morning deep work block from 8am to noon with no exceptions
[x] Email and messages only after noon each day
[x] Scheduled shallow work window in the afternoon
[x] Shutdown ritual with a verbal phrase to close the workday
[ ] Full digital sabbath one day per week, still working on this

